query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, s.pricingType, COUNT(pt.id) as tier_count 
FROM services s 
LEFT JOIN pricingTiers pt ON s.id = pt.serviceId 
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Airbnb%' OR s.nameEn LIKE '%Service Apartments%'
GROUP BY s.id;
